rabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013196, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Peace of Allah be upon Muhammad the Messenger of Allah, the trustee of Allah over His Revelations, Messages, and determined commandments, the core of the Divine Inspiration and Revelation, who sealed the previous Messages, paved the way to the coming blessings, who prevails over all that, the witness over the creatures, and the luminous torch. Peace and Allah’s mercy and blessings be upon him.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Khuda ki taraf se salaam ho Khuda ke Rasool Hazrat Muhammad (s.a.w.a) par jo Khuda ki wahi aur uske paighaamo’n aur ehkaam'e deen ke ameen hai. Wahi o aayaat ke khazeene-daar hai, nabiyyo’n ke khaatim, uloom'e aasmaani ke bayaan karne waale aur tamaam maaddi (materialistic) wa roohaani uloom ke muhaafiz hai, makhlooq par gawah wa shaahid, roshni phaila ne waale chiraagh hai. Salaam ho Aan Hazrat (s.a.w.a) par Khuda ki rehmat ho aur Uski barkate’n.", "Urdu": "خدا کی طرف سے سلام ہو خدا کے رسول حضرت محمدؐ پر جو خدا کی وحی اور اس کے پیغاموں اور احکام ِدین کے امین ہیں وحی و آیات کے خزانہ دار ہیں نبیوں کے خاتم علوم ِآسمانی کے بیان کرنے والے اور تمام مادی و روحانی علوم کے محافظ ہیں مخلوق پر گواہ و شاہد روشنی پھیلانے والا چراغ ہیں سلام ہو آنحضرتؐ پر خدا کی رحمت ہو اور اس کی برکتیں۔", "RArabic": "AS-SALAAMO MENAL LAAHE A’LAA MOHAMMADIN RASOOLIL LAAHE AMEENIL LAAHE A’LAA WAHYE-HI WA RESAALAATE-HI WA A’ZAAA'e ME AMRE-HI WA MA’DENIL WAHYE WA WAT TANZEE-LIL KHAATE-ME LEMAA SABAQA WAL FAATE-HE LEMAS-TUQBELA WAL MO-HAIY-MENE A’LAA ZAALE-KA KULLE-HISH SHAAHEDE A’LAL KHALQIS SERAAJIL MONEERE WAS-SALAAMO A’LAY-HE WA RAHMA-TUL LAAHE WA BARA-KAATO-HU.", "ArabicText1": "اَلسَّلَامُ مِنَ اللہِ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ رَسُوْلِ اللہِ اَمِیْنِ اللہِ عَلٰی وَحْیِهٖ وَرِسَالَاتِهٖ وَعَزَآئِمِ اَمْرِهٖ وَمَعْدِ", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": " نِ", "ArabicText2": "الْوَحْیِ وَ التَّنْزِیْلِ الْخَاتِمِ لِمَا سَبَقَ وَالْفَاتِحِ لِمَا اسْتُقْبِلَ وَالْمُهَیْمِنِ عَلٰی ذٰلِكَ كُلِّهِ الشَّاهِدِ عَلَی الْخَلْقِ السِّرَاجِ الْمُنِیْرِ وَالسَّلَامُ عَلَیْهِ وَرَحْمَۃُ اللہِ وَبَرَكَاتُهٗ۔", "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013197, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah, (please do) send blessings upon Muhammad and his Household, the oppressed ones, with the best, most perfect, most exalted, and most honored blessings that You have ever showed on any of Your Prophets, Messengers, and Chosen servants.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Ma’bood! Hazrat Muhammad (s.a.w.a) aur unke Ahlebait (a.s) par rehmat naazil farma jo mazloom hai, behtareen us se kaamil-tar, buland-tar aur buzurg-tar rehmat farma jo Tu ne apne nabiyyo’n, rasoolo’n aur apne pasand kiye huwe mein se kisi par ki hai.", "Urdu": "اے معبود! حضرت محمدؐ اور ان کے اہل بیتؑ پر رحمت نازل فرما جو مظلوم ہیں ان پر بہترین اس سے کامل تر بلند تراور بزرگ تر رحمت فرماجو تو نے اپنے نبیوں اپنے رسولوں اور اپنے پسند کئے ہوؤں میں سے کسی پر کی ہے۔", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA SALLE A’LAA MOHAMMADIN WA AHLE BAYTE-HIL MAZLOO-MEENA AFZALA WA AKMALA WA ARFA-A’ WA ASHRAFA MAA SALLAYTA A’LAA AHA-DIN MIN AMBEYAAA-E-KA WA BE-ROSOLE-KA WA ASFEYAAA-E-KA.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ صَلِّ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ وَّاَهْلِ بَیْتِهِ الْمَظْلُوْمِیْنَ اَفْضَلَ وَاَكْمَلَ وَاَرْفَعَ وَاَشْرَفَ مَا صَلَّیْتَ عَلٰی اَحَدٍ مِّنْ اَنْبِیَآئِكَ وَرُسُلِكَ وَاَصْفِیَآئِكَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013198, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah, (please do) send blessings upon the Commander of the Faithful, Your servant, the best of Your creatures after Your Prophet, the brother of Your Messenger, the Successor of Your most-beloved one, whom You have selected from among Your beings, the guide to those whom You sent with Your messages, the establisher of the true religion by means of Your justice, and the decisive judge among Your beings. Peace and Allah’s mercy and blessings be upon him.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Ma’bood! Momino ke sardaar par rehmat naazil farma jo Tere bande aur Tere Nabi ke baad saari makhlooq mein behtareen, Tere Rasool ke bhai aur Tere Wasi ke habib hai, keh jin ko Tu ne apni makhlooq ke darmiyaan se choona, woh rehnumaayi karte hai us hasti ki taraf jise Tu ne apna paighambar banaya woh qayaamat mein Tere adl se jaza dene waale aur Teri makhlooq mein insaaf ka faisla karne waale hai. Salaam ho Ameerul Momeneen (a.s) par aur Khuda ki rehmat ho aur uski barkate’n.", "Urdu": "اے معبود! مومنوں کے سردار پر رحمت نازل فرما جو تیرے بندے اور تیرے نبیؐ کے بعد ساری مخلوق میں بہترین تیرے رسولؐ کے بھائی اور تیرے وصی کے حبیب ہیں کہ جن کو تو نے اپنی مخلوق کے درمیان سے چنا وہ رہنمائی کرتے ہیں اس ہستی کی طرف جسے تو نے اپنا پیغمبر بنایا وہ قیامت میں تیرے عدل سے جزا دینے والے اور تیری مخلوق میں انصاف کا فیصلہ کرنے والے ہیں سلام ہو امیر المؤمنین ؑپر اور خدا کی رحمت ہو اور اس کی برکتیں۔", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA SALLE A’LAA AMEERIL MOMINEENA AB’DEKA WA KHAYRE KHALQE-KA BA’DA NABIYYE-KA WA AKHEE RASOOLE-KA WA WASIYYE HABEEBE-KAL LAZIN-TAJABTA-HU MIN KHALQE-KA WAD-DALEELE A’LAA MAN BA-A’S-TAHU BE-RESAA-LAATE-KA WA DAYYAA-NID DEENE BE-A’DLE-KA WA FASLE QAZAAA-E-KA BAYNA KHALQE-KA WAS-SALAAMO A’LAIHE WA RAHMATUL LAAHE WA BARA-KAATO-HU.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ صَلِّ عَلٰی اَمِیْرِ الْمُؤْمِنِیْنَ عَبْدِكَ وَخَیْرِ خَلْقِكَ بَعْدَ نَبِیِّكَ وَاَخِیْ رَسُوْلِكَ وَوَصِیِّ حَبِیْبِكَ الَّذِیْ انْتَجَبْتَهٗ مِنْ خَلْقِكَ وَالدَّلِیْلِ عَلٰی مَنْۢ بَعَثْتَهٗ بِرِسَالَاتِكَ وَدَیَّانِ الدِّیْنِ بِعَدْلِكَ وَفَصْلِ قَضَآئِكَ بَیْنَ خَلْقِكَ وَالسَّلَامُ عَلَیْهِ وَرَحْمَۃُ اللہِ وَ بَرَكَاتُهٗ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013199, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah, (please do) send blessings upon the Imams from his offspring, (who are) the holders of Your commandments after him, and the immaculate ones whom You have accepted as supporters of Your religion, keepers of Your secret, witnesses over Your created beings, and signs (of example) for Your servants. May Your blessings be upon them all.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Ma’bood! Un Aimma (a.s) par rehmat farma jo unki aulaad se hai keh unke baad Tere umoor'e deen ko qaaem rakhne waale hai woh paak o paakeeza hai jin ko Tu ne apne deen ki nusrat ke liye pasand farmaaya woh Tere israar ke muhaafiz, Tere makhlooq par gawah o shaahid aur Tere bando’n ke liye nishaan'e hidaayat hai, Teri rehmate’n ho un sab par.", "Urdu": "اے معبود! ان ائمہ پر رحمت فرماجو ان کی اولاد سے ہیں کہ ان کے بعد تیرے امرِ دین کو قائم رکھنے والے ہیں وہ پاک وپاکیزہ ہیں جن کو تو نے اپنے دین کی نصرت کے لئے پسند فرمایا وہ تیرے اسرار کے محافظ تیری مخلوق پر گواہ وشاہد اور تیرے بندوں کے لئے نشانِ ہدایت ہیں تیری رحمتیں ہوں ان سب پر۔", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA SALLE A’LAL A-IMMATE MIN WULDE-HIL QAWWAA-MEENA BE-AMREKA MIN BA’DE-HIL MOTAH-HAREE-NAL LAZEE-NAR TAZAIYTA-HUM ANSAA-RAN LE-DEENE-KA WA HAFA-ZATAN LE SIRRE-KA WA SHOHADAAA-A A’LAA KHALQE-KA WA AA’LAA-MAN LE-E’BAADE-KA SALAWAA-TOKA A’LAIY-HIM AJMA-EE’N.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ صَلِّ عَلَی الْاَئِمَّۃِ مِنْ وُلْدِهِ الْقَوَّامِیْنَ بِاَمْرِكَ مِنْۢ بَعْدِهِ الْمُطَهَّرِیْنَ الَّذِیْنَ ارْتَضَیْتَهُمْ اَنْصَارًا لِدِیْنِكَ وَحَفَظَۃً لِسِرِّكَ وَشُهَدَآءَ عَلٰی خَلْقِكَ وَاَعْلَامًا لِعِبَادِكَ صَلَوَاتُكَ عَلَیْهِمْ اَجْمَعِیْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013200, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Peace be upon the Commander of the Faithful, Ali the son of Abu Talib, the successor of Allah’s Messenger, his representative, who managed his affairs after him, and the master of all Prophet’s successors. May Allah’s mercy and blessings be upon him, too. Peace be upon Fatima, the daughter of Allah’s Messenger, may Allah’s blessings be upon him, (she is) the leader of all the women of this world.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Salaam ho Ameerul Momeneen Ali ibne Abi Talib (a.s) par jo Rasool'e Khuda (s.a.w.a) ke Wasi, unke ja-nasheen aur unke baad unki zimme daariya’n nibha ne waale aur Ausiya ke sardaar hai. Khuda ki rehmat ho un par aur Uski barkate’n. Salaam ho Janab'e Fatema (s.a) par jo Khuda ke Rasool ki dukhtar, tamaam jahano’n ki aurto’n ki sardaar hai.", "Urdu": "سلام ہو امیر المومنین علیؑ ابن ابی طالبؑ پر جو رسولؐ ِخدا کے وصی ان کے جانشین اور ان کے بعد ان کی ذمہ داریاں نبھانے والے اور اوصیاء کے سردار ہیں خدا کی رحمت ہو ان پر اور اس کی برکتیں سلام ہو جناب فاطمہؑ پر جو خدا کے رسولؐ کی دختر تمام جہانوں کی عورتوں کی سردار ہیں۔", "RArabic": "AS-SALAAMO A’LAA AMEERIL MOMENEENA A’LIY-YIBNE ABEE TAALE-BIN WASIYYE RASOOLIL LAAHE WA KHALEE-FATE-HI WAL QAAA'e ME BE-AMRE-HI MIN BAA’DE-HI SAYYEDIL WASIYYEEN WA RAHMATUL LAAHE WA BARA-KAATO-HU. AS-SALAAMO A’LAA FAATE-MATA BINTE RASOOLIL LAAHE SALLAL LAAHO A’LAIHE WA AALEHI SAYYE-DATE NESAAA-IL AA’LAMEENA.", "ArabicText1": "اَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰی اَمِیْرِ الْمُؤْمِنِیْنَ عَلِیِّ بْنِ اَبِیْطَالِبٍ وَصِیِّ رَسُوْلِ اللہِ وَ خَلِیْفَتِهٖ وَالْقَآئِمِ بِاَمْرِهٖ مِنْۢ بَعْدِهٖ سَیِّدِ الْوَصِیِّیْنَ وَرَحْمَۃُ اللہِ وَبَرَكَاتُهٗ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰی فَاطِمَۃَ بِنْتِ رَسُوْلِ اللہِ صَلَّی اللہُ عَلَیْهِ وَاٰلِهٖ سَیِّدَۃِ نِسَآءِ الْعَالَمِیْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013201, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Peace be upon Hasan and Husain, the chiefs of the youth of Paradise among all beings. Peace be upon the Guiding Imams. Peace be upon the Prophets and the Messengers. Peace be upon the Imams whom are entrusted (with the religion by Allah).", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Salaam ho Hazrat Hasan (a.s) wa Hazrat Husain (a.s) par, jo dono, saari makhlooq mein se jawaanane Jannat ke sardaar hai. Salaam ho hidaayat dene waale Aimma (a.s) par. Salaam ho tamaam nabiyyo’n aur rasoolo’n par. Salaam ho un Aimma (a.s) par jin ko nabuwwat ki amaanate’n di gayi.", "Urdu": "سلام ہو حضرت حسنؑ و حسینؑ پر جو دونوں ساری مخلوق میں سے جوانانِ جنت کے سردار ہیں سلام ہو ہدایت دینے والے ائمہ ؑپر سلام ہو تمام نبیوں اور رسولوں پر سلام ہو ان ائمہؑ پر جن کو نبوت کی امانتیں دی گئیں۔", "RArabic": "AS-SALAAMO A’LAL HASANE WAL HUSAIY-NE SAYYEDAIY SHABAABE AHLIL JANNATE MENAL KHALQE AJMA-EE’NA AS-SALAAMO A’LAL A-IMMATIR RAASHE-DEENA AS-SALAAMO A’LAL AMBEYAAA-E WAL MURSALEENA AS-SALAAMO A’LAL A-IMMATIL MUSTAWDE-EE’NA.", "ArabicText1": "اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَی الْحَسَنِ وَالْحُسَیْنِ سَیِّدَیْ شَبَابِ اَهْلِ الْجَنَّۃِ مِنَ الْخَلْقِ اَجْمَعِیْنَ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَی الْاَئِمَّۃِ الرَّاشِدِیْنَ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَی الْاَنْبِیَآءِ وَالْمُرْسَلِیْنَ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَی الْاَئِمَّۃِ الْمُسْتَوْدِعِیْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013202, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Peace be upon the elite creatures of Allah. Peace be upon those who understand by tokens. Peace be upon the faithful believers who have carried out His orders, supported the saints of Allah, and have feared for their fear. Peace be upon the Favorite Angels. Peace be upon us and upon the righteous servants of Allah.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Salaam ho un par jo makhlooq mein se Khuda ke khaas hai. Salaam ho saahebaan'e aql wa khird par. Salaam ho un momino par Khuda ke hukm par kaar-band (amal pehra) huwe, Khuda ke auliya ke madad-gaar bane aur unke khouf mein khaaef hai. Salaam ho muqarrab (qareebi) baargah'e farishto’n par. Salaam ho ham par aur Khuda ke nek aur khush kirdaar bando’n par.", "Urdu": "سلام ہو ان پر جو مخلوق میں سے خاصان ِخدا ہیں سلام ہوصاحبانِ عقل وخرد پر سلام ہو ان مومنوں پر جو حکم ِخدا پر کاربند ہوئے خدا کے اولیاء کے مددگار بنے اور ان کے خوف میں خوف زدہ ہیں سلام ہو مقربِ بارگاہ فرشتوں پر سلام ہوہم پر اور خدا کے نیک اور خوش کردار بندوں پر۔", "RArabic": "AS-SALAAMO A’LAA KHAAASSA-TIL LAAHE MIN KHALQE-HI AS-SALAAMO A’LAL MOTAWASSE-MEENA AS-SALAAMO A’LAL MOMENEE-NAL LAZEENA QAAMOO BE-AMRE-HI WA WAA-ZAROO AWLEYAAA-AL LAAHE WA KHAAFOO BE-KHAWFE-HIM. AS-SALAAMO A’LAL MALAAA'e KATIL MOQARRA-BEENA. AS-SALAAMO A’LAYNAA WA A’LAA E’BAA-DIL LAAHIS SAALE-HEENA.", "ArabicText1": "اَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰی خَآصَّۃِ اللہِ مِنْ خَلْقِهٖ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَی الْمُتَوَسِّمِیْنَ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَی الْمُؤْمِنِیْنَ الَّذِیْنَ قَامُوْا بِاَمْرِهٖ وَ وَازَرُوْا اَوْلِیَآءَ اللہِ وَ خَافُوْا بِخَوْفِهِمْ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَی الْمَلَآئِكَۃِ الْمُقَرَّبِیْنَ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْنَا وَعَلٰی عِبَادِ اللہِ الصَّالِحِیْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null,